bio: Sogrlaf is a Nord sailor who can be found in Windhelm Docks on the ship Northern Maiden. He works for captain Gjalund Salt-Sage. After the Dragonborn has sailed to Solstheim, Sogrlaf can be found on the Northern Maiden in Raven Rock. He wears a farm outift, carries some gold and is equipped with a Steel Dagger.
name: Sogrlaf
